      "id": "PopularPost222084",
      "post_content": "This is truly awful in multiplayer.  \n  \nPro: You can destroy ten lands for the price of one, in a large enough game. That makes Tremble the most efficient land destruction card ever printed in the history of (multiplayer) magic.  \n  \nCon: You effectively receive an emblem with \"Creatures opponents control attack you each turn if able. Spells opponents control target you if their effect is nasty. Any number of players may decide to not invite you to lunch at end of game.\"",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost222084\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">This is truly awful in multiplayer.<br/><br/>Pro: You can destroy ten lands for the price of one, in a large enough game. That makes Tremble the most efficient land destruction card ever printed in the history of (multiplayer) magic.<br/><br/>Con: You effectively receive an emblem with \"Creatures opponents control attack you each turn if able. Spells opponents control target you if their effect is nasty. Any number of players may decide to not invite you to lunch at end of game.\"</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '222084'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67559\">Salient</span>\r\n                                (5/2/2012 7:20:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png