    {
      "id": "PopularPost185664",
      "post_content": "Use with [Flagstones of Trokair](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flagstones of Trokair), [Gods' Eye, Gate to the Reikai](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gods' Eye, Gate to the Reikai), or even [Dakmor Salvage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dakmor Salvage).  \n  \n[Raze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raze) is usually preferable though - it costs ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol) less and you even get to choose the land.  \nUnless your opponent's land are all either [consecrated](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=108801), [fortified](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=126211) with or even [made of](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=45415) Darksteel. Which is *very* unlikely.  \n  \nAnd even if Raze gets countered it ain't that bad if you still just get to search a Plains. (The 1/1 spirit or the ability to Dredge might not be always that preferable to your land, but that likely won't make you worry as often as paying more mana or not being able to choose their [Rishadan Port](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rishadan Port), [Mishra's Factory](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mishra's Factory) or [Contested Cliffs](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Contested Cliffs).)",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost185664\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Use with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Flagstones of Trokair\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flagstones of Trokair\">Flagstones of Trokair</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gods' Eye, Gate to the Reikai\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gods' Eye, Gate to the Reikai\">Gods' Eye, Gate to the Reikai</a>, or even <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dakmor Salvage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dakmor Salvage\">Dakmor Salvage</a>.<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Raze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raze\">Raze</a> is usually preferable though - it costs <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/> less and you even get to choose the land.<br/>Unless your opponent's land are all either <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"108801\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=108801\">consecrated</a>,  <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"126211\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=126211\">fortified</a> with or even <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"45415\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=45415\">made of</a> Darksteel. Which is <i>very</i> unlikely.<br/><br/>And even if Raze gets countered it ain't that bad if you still just get to search a Plains. (The 1/1 spirit or the ability to Dredge might not be always that preferable to your land, but that likely won't make you worry as often as paying more mana or not being able to choose their <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Rishadan Port\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rishadan Port\">Rishadan Port</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mishra's Factory\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mishra's Factory\">Mishra's Factory</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Contested Cliffs\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Contested Cliffs\">Contested Cliffs</a>.)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '185664'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (8/6/2011 6:09:01 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
